headline.print_headline: Williams and Halep Advance to Final
headline.main: Williams and Halep Advance to Final

lead_paragraph: Serena Williams, her insatiable will to win as strong as ever, regained her composure after smashing her racquet and being on the brink of defeat to beat Caroline Wozniacki 2-6 6-3 7-6(6) on Saturday and reach the title match at the WTA Finals.
